{"tid":1488343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺[勇武派]都係得[勇]而沒有[武]","createTime":"2019-08-19T15:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T01:13:59.000Z","uid":165288,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f6d4644651f1a3c2dff4eb7e18447589bb4efe73","tid":1488343,"uid":165288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"其實如果要發夢去要武力抗爭，起碼大家身上最少都有把行山仗啦，發覺好多勇武手上乜武器都冇。就算真係乜都冇，發夢點都要起磚，唔係點反擊或防衛?<br />\n<br />\n如果狗冇出槍嘅大前題下<br />\n有比警棍更長嘅野其實速龍都唔駛驚。齊馬嘅話，速龍衝埋嚟，你發夢時不斷向前篤，佢仲傷過你。<br />\n但最少一排2-3十人都要有長野就好安全，第二排就拉實第一排嘅背包，唔好被狗拉走。<br />\n其實發夢只是鬥多人嘅遊戲，唔能夠次次都比狗有時間部署，有機會一定要先主動攻散班狗部署，最簡單嘅做法就係不斷擲野。<br />\n<br />\n再者，如果乜都冇真係寧願一早退後少少遊擊下算。"},{"pid":"27625ae472e901a2c17b4adc5ad73d4d4ae3263e","tid":1488343,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6a0ed26ce2c5c69fecc74a17667e4d6da2e71f8d","tid":1488343,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"行山杖就真係要<br />\n元朗個次幾有效<br />\n埋身時都有得用下"},{"pid":"7694efbfe4765429427ef38bd168c379fedeb678","tid":1488343,"uid":165288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a0ed26ce2c5c69fecc74a17667e4d6da2e71f8d","tid":1488343,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"行山杖就真係要<br />\n元朗個次幾有效<br />\n埋身時都有得用下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"但宜家淘行山仗都唔得，我試過. lock 咗"},{"pid":"bb15873671a62299266c8161a8ed34f336cf6d0f","tid":1488343,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7694efbfe4765429427ef38bd168c379fedeb678","tid":1488343,"uid":165288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a0ed26ce2c5c69fecc74a17667e4d6da2e71f8d","tid":1488343,"uid":141419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"行山杖就真係要<br />\n元朗個次幾有效<br />\n埋身時都有得用下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"但宜家淘行山仗都唔得，我試過. lock 咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"運動鋪有<br />\n淘寶好易彎<br />\n大力小小一中膠盾就88"},{"pid":"46338bca19b1109764f03be54e54b6032870f00e","tid":1488343,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:43:55.000Z","msg":"但係大家都仲未有同狗真正開仗嘅覺悟呢"},{"pid":"64996a80909b88d25ecc285f2f1267497cfdc8b2","tid":1488343,"uid":201170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:45:23.000Z","msg":"迪卡儂有 唔好買64蚊 買貴啲 不過宜家唔翻貨 要買就快"},{"pid":"915334e3d5e43354fe5951a9db35d98395213738","tid":1488343,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:45:47.000Z","msg":"其實係驚啫 根本都夠打"},{"pid":"d22376ae180055ce55b56467c115f5f317f90729","tid":1488343,"uid":165288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"915334e3d5e43354fe5951a9db35d98395213738","tid":1488343,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:45:47.000Z","msg":"其實係驚啫 根本都夠打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T00:39:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/803879953032830?view=permalink&amp;id=2392500350837441\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F803879953032830%3Fview%3Dpermalink%26id%3D2392500350837441&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAPsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=8ce7af06\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/groups/803879953032830?view=permalink&amp;id=2392500350837441</a><br />\n<br />\n我數住唔只30人跑過，40-50 都有，但最尾係得5-7個速龍，可能隨後仲有一隊防暴就唔知。呢個情況其實乜都冇都可以落佢地單啦，40人圍7個都唔夠打?<br />\n閘即使唔發夢圍毆佢，起初得兩個速龍，每個位跑過飛腳佢地，都冇得開槍或捉人。<br />\n但個個驚到係咁走"},{"pid":"fffc8cdb0b60bcb2e1bfcec44510271a6b2d7652","tid":1488343,"uid":165288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u5RhBrT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu5RhBrT.png&h=f3984dce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行山仗買唔到，可以呢啲，單枝式腳架。<br />\n雙向用都得，個尾扑嘅話好夠力"}]}